{"tid":2108660,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"口罩令有否侵犯自由？","createTime":"2020-07-14T16:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T17:24:56.000Z","uid":277788,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"43b0e87f083f27d46387a3c163ab3202479351ae","tid":2108660,"uid":277788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:47:27.000Z","msg":"美國都討論緊自由 香港係咪都要有？唔戴口罩係我地人權自由，宜家既運動唔係都追求緊大家既自由咩！口罩令是否侵犯了香港人既自由？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/496555?utm_source=01appshare&amp;utm_medium=referral\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F496555%3Futm_source%3D01appshare%26utm_medium%3Dreferral&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuMg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=39beb4b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/496555?utm_source=01appshare&amp;utm_medium=referral</a>"},{"pid":"68cf86527a7d424db626691f2e1c69d23afb6ed3","tid":2108660,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:48:43.000Z","msg":"先定義普世價值"},{"pid":"e61b3e22ad61821956c2259a0162486961028ddb","tid":2108660,"uid":271250,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:55:05.000Z","msg":"你話醉酒駕駛犯唔犯法？之所以犯法，係因為醉駕有好大機會傷到人；同樣道理，唔戴口罩就易賴嘢，賴到嘢又易傳比人。你話犯唔犯法？（答返你個問題，口罩令係侵犯自由，但推出政策，個人自由非唯一需要考慮嘅嘢，整體利益都好重要，如果只考慮自由，建立群體社會呢件事，本身就係錯既）"},{"pid":"aa0c05c0e92d2af9887db1f141f81cae2a3dfb41","tid":2108660,"uid":50429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T17:06:02.000Z","msg":"Harm principle <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89edf12c551ef72baeed9d6e81788df13741a2e1","tid":2108660,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T17:24:56.000Z","msg":"問吓<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong><em>林鄭月娥</em></strong></span></span>"}]}